reviewText: Of course I'm giving this 5 stars, I went to Michigan and graduated in 1989!

I HAVE BEEN A "UNIVERSITY OF MICHIGAN" FAN ALL MY LIFE. I HAD EYE SURGERY THE WEEK BEFORE THE 1989 CHAMPIONSHIP GAME. I COULD NOT SEE THE T.V. PICTURE, BUT I LISTENED TO THE COMMENTARY. FOR MANY YEARS I HAVE WANTED TO SEE THE GAME. I LOVE THE DVD......BECAUSE THE GAME GOES OVERTIME AND "MICHIGAN" WINS!!
